Package it.polimi.ingsw.network.objects

Class NetDivinityChoice

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.network.objects.NetObject
it.polimi.ingsw.network.objects.NetDivinityChoice
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class NetDivinityChoice
extends NetObject
This class is a class used to exchange messages between clients and server in the gods phase of the game where challenger chooses gods and the starter and players choose a god. More information about game phase can be found on it.polimi.ingsw.core.state package.
